<p>ã“ã“ã§</p>

\[F 
= \frac{1}{C_P T_0} \left. \left( \frac{\partial \epsilon}{\partial T} - \frac{\partial \epsilon_\mathrm{rad}}{\partial T}\right) \right|_{T_0} \tag{17}\]

<p>ã§ã™ã€‚
