\[\epsilon_\rho 
\sim 1, \quad \kappa_\rho 
\sim 1, \quad \kappa_T 
\sim 0, \quad \epsilon 
\simeq \epsilon_\mathrm{rad} \tag{29}\]

<p>ãŒè‰¯ã„è¿‘ä¼¼ã¨ã—ã¦æˆã‚Šç«‹ã¡ã¾ã™ã€‚
